<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.phastmike.tags.desktop</id>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <name>tags</name>
  <summary>Color logs based on tags</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Create tags with color schemes and give color to your logs or text files</p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Load tags</li>
      <li>Save tags</li>
      <li>Remove all tags</li>
      <li>Open new window</li>
      <li>User defined line numbering color scheme</li>
      <li>Simple tags based on string containing a pattern</li>
      <li>Support for regular expressions</li>
      <li>Case sensitive support</li>
      <li>Automic load tags file when opening a file and a similarly named file with added .tags extension exists</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
